headline: Some buy now, pay later lenders are holding back customer payment data from credit bureaus
summary: Major BNPL firms won't report customer data to credit bureaus until they see evidence that responsible payment behavior helps rather than hurts credit scores.

headline: 1 Magnificent Growth Stock Down 43% to Buy and Hold Forever
